==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Monkflower
<hw>Monk"flow`er</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A name of certain curious orchids which bear three kinds of flowers
formerly referred to three genera, but now ascertained to be sexually
different forms of the same genus (<spn>Catasetum tridentatum</spn>,
etc.).</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Monkhood</ent>⟦br⟧
